"668","Item 61"
"669","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"670","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"671","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"672","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"673","semi-monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"674","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"675","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"676","investments under the minimum."
